Step 1:Create Database Connection Object and using cursor() method to execute SQL Queries:

mydb = mysql.connector.connect(host="localhost",user="yourusername",passwd="yourpassword")
mycursor = mydb.cursor()

Step 2: Create Database
mycursor.execute("CREATE DATABASE database_name")

Step 3: Show Database
mycursor.execute("SHOW DATABASES")

Step 4: Run 
python demo_create_db.py